# pipenv
#   According to pypa/pipenv#598, it is recommended to include Pipfile.lock in version control.
#   However, in case of collaboration, if having platform-specific dependencies or dependencies
#   having no cross-platform support, pipfile.lock left out may be a good alternative.
#   Of course, this is a trade-off between the convenience of the current automated CI and the
#   robustness of the dependency resolution.
# /Pipfile.lock

# PEP 582; used by e.g. github.com/David-O-Toole/proofit404
__pypackages__/

